<p>This website is dedicated to renting Virtual Private Servers (VPS) for setting up VPNs.</p>
<p>Here, you will find information on selecting, configuring, and using VPS to protect personal data, bypass restrictions, and ensure online anonymity.</p>

<h4>What is a VPS?</h4>
<p>A VPS (Virtual Private Server) is a virtual server that operates like a standalone computer but is hosted on a powerful physical server.</p>

<h4>Why use a VPS for VPN?</h4>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Bypass restrictions</strong> — access websites without limitations.</li>
    <li><strong>Security</strong> — data encryption and protection against leaks.</li>
    <li><strong>Anonymity</strong> — hide your real IP address.</li>
    <li><strong>Flexibility</strong> — ability to install required software.</li>
</ul>

<p>The website provides guides on choosing a VPS provider, setting up a VPN server, and security recommendations.</p>